Definition. Let  $\nu = \nu^{+} - \nu^{-}$  be the Jordan decomposition of  $\nu$ . The total variation of  $\nu$  is the positive measure  $|\nu|$  defined by

$$
| \nu | = \nu^ {+} + \nu^ {-}.
$$

